The paper deals with optimizing the write fidelity of MRAMs, which is a topic related to electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET), as well as optimization and control theory (cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.IT). The proposed approach involves using a biconvex optimization method, which is a common technique in machine learning and optimization (cs.NE).
